<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Locked on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/locked/</link><description>Recent content in Locked on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/locked/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] macOS Apple ID Sign-In Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/macos/macos-apple-id-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/macos/macos-apple-id-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="macos-apple-id-sign-in-error-fix"&gt;macOS Apple ID Sign-In Error Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apple ID sign-in errors prevent you from accessing iCloud, App Store, and other Apple services. Messages include &amp;ldquo;Verification Failed,&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;Apple ID Locked,&amp;rdquo; or &amp;ldquo;An error occurred during activation.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apple ID authentication requires a valid session token and network connection to Apple&amp;rsquo;s authentication servers. Failures can be due to incorrect credentials, two-factor authentication issues, or server-side problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorrect Apple ID password&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Two-factor authentication code expired or incorrect&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apple ID locked due to too many failed attempts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Date/time incorrect preventing SSL validation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network blocking Apple authentication servers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;macOS keychain corruption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="1-check-apple-id-status"&gt;1. Check Apple ID status&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Verify Apple ID is not disabled&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Visit https://iforgot.apple.com from another device&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Check system date/time&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;date
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo sntp -sS time.apple.com
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="2-reset-keychain-for-apple-id"&gt;2. Reset keychain for Apple ID&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Open Keychain Access (Applications → Utilities)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Search for &amp;#34;appleid&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Delete all entries related to Apple ID&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Restart the Mac and sign in again&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="3-sign-in-via-terminal"&gt;3. Sign in via terminal&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Check Apple ID account status via System Configuration&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;defaults read /Library/Preferences/SystemConfiguration/com.apple.airport.preferences
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="4-clear-authentication-cache"&gt;4. Clear authentication cache&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Clear the authentication agent cache&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo defaults delete /Library/Preferences/com.apple.loginwindow RetriesUntilBlank
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;killall AccountsDaemon
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="macos-icloud-error"&gt;iCloud Error&lt;/a&gt; — iCloud sync failures after auth issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="keychain-error"&gt;Keychain Error&lt;/a&gt; — keychain access and unlock errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="nserror-10"&gt;App Store Error&lt;/a&gt; — App Store download failures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Record locked</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/locked-record/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/locked-record/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A record locked error (FILE-STATUS 42) occurs when a program tries to access a record that has been locked by another process. This is common in multi-user environments where multiple programs access the same file.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Another process has locked the record&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing unlock operation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transaction not completed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deadlock between processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PROCEDURE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DIVISION&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; MAIN-PROCEDURE.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OPEN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;I-O&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;RECORD&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IS&lt;/span&gt; LOCKED&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DISPLAY &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Record locked by another user&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CLOSE&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;STOP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;RUN
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-READ
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WRITE&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-RECORD&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UNLOCK&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PROCEDURE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DIVISION&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Retry with delay
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MOVE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TO&lt;/span&gt; WS-RETRY-COUNT&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PERFORM&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UNTIL&lt;/span&gt; WS-RETRY-COUNT &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;RECORD&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IS&lt;/span&gt; LOCKED&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TO&lt;/span&gt; WS-RETRY-COUNT&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CALL &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;C$SLEEP&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;USING&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;RECORD&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IS&lt;/span&gt; LOCKED&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;EXIT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PERFORM
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-READ
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-PERFORM
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Example 1: Lock conflict
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OPEN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;I-O&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * FILE-STATUS = 42 (locked)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Example 2: Missing unlock
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OPEN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;I-O&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WRITE&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-RECORD&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Record still locked
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Example 3: Deadlock
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Program A locks record 1, waits for record 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Program B locks record 2, waits for record 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/file-status"&gt;File status error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/end-of-file"&gt;End of file&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>SQLite - database is locked (BUSY)</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/sqlite-database-locked-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/sqlite-database-locked-v2/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;SQLite &amp;ldquo;database is locked (SQLITE_BUSY)&amp;rdquo; error occurs when a connection tries to access a database that is currently locked by another connection. This is common in concurrent applications where multiple connections try to write simultaneously.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Another connection holding a write lock&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Long-running transaction preventing other access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Default busy timeout too short&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using journal mode instead of WAL for concurrency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple processes accessing the same database file&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set a busy timeout:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;conn &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;connect(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;mydb.sqlite&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, timeout&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wait up to 30 seconds for lock to be released&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable WAL (Write-Ahead Logging) mode for better concurrency:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;PRAGMA journal_mode&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;WAL;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;PRAGMA busy_timeout&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use connection pooling with proper timeout:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sqlite3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;require&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;sqlite3&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;verbose&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sqlite3&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Database&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;mydb.sqlite&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sqlite3&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;OPEN_READWRITE&lt;/span&gt;, (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt;) =&amp;gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;message&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;configure&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;busyTimeout&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30000&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Close connections promptly after use:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;conn &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;connect(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;mydb.sqlite&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; conn&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;execute(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;INSERT INTO users VALUES (1, &amp;#34;John&amp;#34;)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; conn&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;commit()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;finally&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; conn&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;close() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Always close in finally block&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="5"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use single connection per process:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Create a single connection per process&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; threading
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;local &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; threading&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;local()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;get_connection&lt;/span&gt;():
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;not&lt;/span&gt; hasattr(local, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;conn&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; local&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;conn &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;connect(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;mydb.sqlite&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, timeout&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; local&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;conn
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="6"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check WAL mode status:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sqlite3 mydb.sqlite &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;PRAGMA journal_mode;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Should return: wal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;conn &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;connect(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;mydb.sqlite&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cursor &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; conn&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;cursor()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error: database is locked&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cursor&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;execute(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;INSERT INTO users VALUES (1, &amp;#34;John&amp;#34;)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Fix: set timeout&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;conn &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;connect(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;mydb.sqlite&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, timeout&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Set WAL mode for better concurrency
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;PRAGMA journal_mode&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;WAL;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;PRAGMA busy_timeout&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10000&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;John&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/sqlite-connection-error/"&gt;Connection error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/sqlite-constraint-error/"&gt;Constraint error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>SQLite Database Locked</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/sqlite-database-locked/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/sqlite-database-locked/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="sqlite-database-locked"&gt;SQLite Database Locked&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;SQLITE_BUSY&lt;/code&gt; error occurs when SQLite cannot acquire a lock on the database because another connection or process already holds a conflicting lock. SQLite uses file-level locking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Another process holds a write lock&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Long-running transaction blocking others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;WAL file locked by another process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Concurrent write attempts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="increase-busy-timeout"&gt;Increase Busy Timeout&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;PRAGMA busy_timeout &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-for-locking-processes"&gt;Check for Locking Processes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;lsof your_database.db
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-wal-mode"&gt;Use WAL Mode&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;PRAGMA journal_mode&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;WAL;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="close-connections-properly"&gt;Close Connections Properly&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;conn &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;connect(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;mydb.sqlite&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; conn&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;execute(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;INSERT INTO users VALUES (1, &amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; conn&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;commit()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;finally&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; conn&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;close()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-connection-pooling"&gt;Use Connection Pooling&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; contextlib &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; contextmanager
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@contextmanager&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;get_connection&lt;/span&gt;():
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; conn &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;connect(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;mydb.sqlite&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;yield&lt;/span&gt; conn
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;finally&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; conn&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;close()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Terminal 1: starts a transaction
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BEGIN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IMMEDIATE&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Terminal 2: tries to write
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Alice&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error: SQLITE_BUSY: database is locked
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/sqlite-connection-error/"&gt;Connection Error&lt;/a&gt; — connection failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/io-error2/"&gt;I/O Error&lt;/a&gt; — I/O error&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>